Now there's an easy way for speedy ticket counter
to ticket counter delivery of your important parcels.
Air California's Jet-Pac is the fastest and most
reliable way to ship small parcels.
Whether it's a cost estimate, vital spare part, sales
bid or legal document, Jet-Pac can rush it to any
Air California city within hours.
Any parcel which weighs 15 pounds or less, and
doesn't exceed three feet in any single dimension
(length, width or height), qualifies for Jet-Pac
services. It must be delivered to the Air California
Ticket Counter at the point of departure at least
30 minutes before take off of the specified flight.
Jet-Pac assures shipment of your parcel on a
specified flight. Recipients can collect the
shipment at the Air California Ticket Counter at the
destination. It's unloaded first and rushed to the
counter as soon as the plane's baggage doors
are opened.
